 (352,9,500,'Core Probs African-Am Studies',349,'Introduction for grad students to the central concepts, theories, methodologies, and paradigms in Black Studies.  Students will also be introduced to the key critical scholars, seminal works and emerging trends in Black Studies.  Prerequisite: Graduate standing.'),
