 (2096,57,541,'Computer Systems Analysis',2011,'Same as CSE 524 and ECE 541.  See ECE 541.'),
 (2097,57,542,'Artificial Neural Networks',2012,'Comprehensive treatment of neural network architectures and learning algorithms balanced with theory and application examples. Prerequisite: CS 440, MATH 385, and MATH 415.'),
