 (2895,71,465,'Stage Comedy',2152,'History and theory of stage comedy. Same as CWL 465. 3 undergraduate hours. 4 graduate hours.  Prerequisite: One year of college literature, or consent of instructor.'),
 (2896,71,466,'Topics in Modern Drama',2646,'3 undergraduate hours. 4 graduate hours. May be repeated if topics vary.  Prerequisite: One year of college literature, or consent of instructor.'),
