 (5163,118,583,'Laboratory Rotation III',4473,'Laboratory research methods; familiarization of first-year graduate students with experimental methods used in research in microbiology. Required of all first-year students majoring in microbiology. Third five weeks of each term.   Approved for S/U grading only.  Prerequisite: First-year graduate status and consent of department; concurrent registration in MCB 581 and MCB 582.'),
