 (5596,126,486,'Double Bass',4827,'Instruction in double bass at the advanced undergraduate and graduate level. Music majors must register concurrently in MUS 250. May be repeated to a maximkum of 12 hours. 2 or 3 undergraduate hours, or 2 or 4 graduate hours. (Summer session, 1 or 2 undergraduate or graduate hours.) Prerequisite: Primarily for music majors; junior standing. Passing of an audition is required prior to initial registration in any applied music course as approved by the faculty of the appropriate applied music division.'),
