 (5599,126,489,'Clarinet',4830,'Instruction in clarinet at the advanced undergraduate and graduate level. May be repeated to a maximum of 16 hours. (Summer session, 1 or 2 undergraduate or graduate hours.) Prerequisite: Primarily for music majors; junior standing. Passing of an audition is required prior to initial registration in any applied music course as approved by the faculty of the appropriate applied music division.'),
 (5600,126,490,'Oboe',4831,'Instruction in oboe at the advanced undergraduate and graduate level. May be repeated to a maximum of 16 hours. (Summer session, 1 or 2 undergraduate or graduate hours.) Prerequisite: Primarily for music majors; junior standing. Passing of an audition is required prior to initial registration in any applied music course as approved by the faculty of the appropriate applied music division.'),
 (5601,126,491,'Bassoon',4832,'Instruction in bassoon at the advanced undergraduate and graduate level. May be repeated to a maximum of 16 hours. (Summer session, 1 or 2 undergraduate or graduate hours.) Prerequisite: Primarily for music majors; junior standing. Passing of an audition is required prior to initial registration in any applied music course as approved by the faculty of the appropriate applied music division.');
