 (5671,126,581,'Graduate Level Voice',4902,'May be repeated to a maximum of 20 hours. (Summer, 1 or 2 hours.) Prerequisite: Graduate standing in music, or successful completion of a qualifying audition for the voice faculty.'),
 (5672,126,582,'Graduate Level Organ',4903,'May be repeated to a maximum of 20 hours. (Summer, 1 or 2 hours.) Prerequisite: Selected studies from the masterworks of organ literature. Prerequisite: Graduate standing in music, or successful completion of a qualifying audition for appropriate faculty members of the Organ/Harpsichord Division.');
